&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Improved efficiency and productivity&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;High implementation costs&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enhanced customer experience&lt;/td&gt;
